OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for most, the
OL,6,Fodd light shower, but sunnier over
OL,7,FLochaber, and all areas will brighten
OL,8,Fup with some good sunny spells through
OL,9,Fthe afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,12,Fevening and overnight. Some prolonged
OL,13,Fspells of evening sunshine leading to
OL,14,Fsome clear spells overnight meaning it
OL,15,Fmight feel chilly in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
