OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry with some lengthy sunshine
OL,6,Fto start but soon clouding over for
OL,7,Fthe Western Isles and west coast.
OL,8,FCloud spreading southeast to all
OL,9,Fthrough the afternoon with patchy
OL,10,Flight rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FCloudy
OL,13,Fstart Monday with patchy rain in the
OL,14,Fwest, eastern parts brightening up
OL,15,Fwith some sunshine. Staying cloudy in
OL,16,Fthe west Tuesday and Wednesday with
OL,17,Fbright spells in the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
